M|Mand|tx|\| Phase \| Activities \|
M|Mand|tx|\|-------\|------------\|
M|Mand|tx|\| **1. Task Identification** \| Load PRD (required), TRD (required); optionally Feature Map, ap ds, Data md, Dependency Map; identify value streams \|
M|Mand|| **|define deliverable, set sc criteria, map dependencies, estimate effort (max 16 AI-ag-hours), plan testing, identify risks \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **3. Gate 7 Validation** \| All TRD cp covered; every task delivers working software; measurable sc criteria; correct deps; no task >2 weeks; testing st defined \|
M|Task|tx|\| Size \| AI-ag-hours \| Calendar Duration* \| Scope \|
M|Task|tx|\|------\|----------------\|-------------------\|-------\|
M|Task|tx|\| Small (S) \| 1-4h \| 1-2 days \| Single cp \|
M|Task|tx|\| md (M) \| 4-8h \| 2-4 days \| Few dependencies \|
M|Task|tx|\| Large (L) \| 8-16h \| 1-2 weeks \| Multiple cp \|
M|Task|tx|\| XL (>16h) \| BREAK IT DOWN \| Too large \| Not atomic \|
M|Task|tx|*1.5x multiplier, 90% capacity, 1 developer
